name: Daultay Dofine
Lore: 'Neimoidian Trade Federation captain who gained his current position through political backstabbing and family connections. Not favored by Darth Sidious.',
Text: 'At start of your draw phase, if you have no cards in your Force Pile may activate up to two Force. If your just drawn destiny was a destroyer droid or battle droid, once per turn you may take that card into hand to cancel that destiny and re-draw.',
